{"tid":921474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK No IT！如學校無法添置古代過時設備 須逐項向教育局解釋原因","createTime":"2018-11-29T14:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T04:44:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"17039955d92ffcad6633492b340b25a957673a13","tid":921474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"而在「標準家具和設備參考清單」中則列出共546項的學校「標準項目」。葉批評，當中部分物品不符現代學校需要，如78盒VHS錄影帶、透明膠片高映機等。他又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">如學校無法添置或認為不需要以上物品，還須逐項向教育局解釋原因</span>，及列明會用甚麼設備取代，導致校方重置或重建校舍時花長時間，及大量人力物力處理設備清單。他促局方設立機制，定期檢討校舍標準及設備清單，確保清單與時並進，減低學校在行政及財政上不必要負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181129/bkn-20181129131602239-1129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181129%2Fbkn-20181129131602239-1129_00822_001.html&d=2fkDh5FmsjrViBEEKUDa%2FwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=037ec90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181129/bkn-20181129131602239-1129_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7bad1ae7eaf5394b4723323cb8592464a97b1a5c","tid":921474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7893c0ba97fa6336ab565eadb8b0dfae46a74c0f","tid":921474,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bad1ae7eaf5394b4723323cb8592464a97b1a5c","tid":921474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im